    <li>轨道层：<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Starlink" rel="noopener">Starlink（2025-12 共 9,357 颗）</a>；<a href="https://merics.org/en/report/orbital-geopolitics-chinas-dual-use-space-internet" rel="noopener">MERICS《Orbital geopolitics》</a>；<a href="https://www.fpri.org/article/2025/04/leo-wars-chinas-orbital-challenge-to-the-us-led-digital-order/" rel="noopener">FPRI《LEO Wars》（2025-04）</a>；<a href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2026/03/20/starlink-spacex-musk-geopolitics-war-ukraine-russia-iran/" rel="noopener">Foreign Policy《Starlink Has Privatized Geopolitics》（2026-03）</a>。</li>
